	<div id="aboutus">
		<img src="images/pudong.gif" alt="PuDong" />
		<p>Richter-International – Your Sourcing Partner</p>
		<p>Richter-International is a specialized consultancy firm for international procurement optimization. Core competencies are sourcing services, which are closely connected with global procurement, for example, global sourcing, supplier search and audit in remote markets, professional trips of sourcing executives, market studies or building up sourcing networks.</p>
		<p>There is only little that our experts have not yet realized in the areas of promotional articles, bamboo flooring and lighting products. We help you to improve your procurement to realize immediate and sustainable results. </p>
		<p>Richter-International supports your company in the achievement of sustainable savings which are directly reflected in the company’s profit performance. </p>
		<p>The hierarchical structure of Richter-International in Europe is very low; the major part of the work takes place in China or Middle East. Richter-International employs buyers and designers specialized in engineering as well as in business administration. This structure ensures that our customers do not have to communicate with changing contact persons in Europe. Of course, we are pleased to pass on this advantage to our customers. </p>
		<p>Besides our international consultancy expertise, the access to our sourcing offices in China and United Arab Emirates is also one of our competitive advantages. Our partners in these offices help you in setting up of a cost-efficient and sustainable procurement of OEM materials and services.</p>
		<p>With the support of Richter-International the gates of the international procurement markets are wide open. Use this unique chance, and enhance the competitiveness of your company. </p>
		<p>Convince yourself of our design and sourcing services. We always adapt ourselves to your individual requirements.</p>
